2 (9) THE AGE OF THE CHILD;
3 (10) ANY MILITARY DEPLOYMENT OF A PARENT AND ITS EFFECT, IF
4 ANY, ON THE PARENT–CHILD RELATIONSHIP;
5 (11) ANY PRIOR COURT ORDERS OR AGREEMENTS;
6 (12) EACH PARENT’S ROLE AND TASKS RELATED TO THE CHILD AND
